	* Üstüne yoğurt dökün: counter:hazine -10, counter:ordu 10
	* Brokoliyi yasaklayın: counter:din 10, counter:reaya -5

Uçan Yeniçeriler (card:ucan_yeniceri)
	bearer: character:yeniceriagasi
	weight: 0.2
